</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>But if this man appears in doubt, and looks miserable and sad, this is a sign of her distress and bad circumstances during this period, and there is a possibility that she will lose something she loves or be separated between her and someone from her.  Relatives or friends, while if he gave her something in a dream, it may have been good news that she would be compensated for what happened to her in the past and God would bless her with happiness and peace of mind.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of a strange man's dream for a single woman by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></strong></h2>
<p>The scholar <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> explained that a single woman's vision of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شخص-غريب-في-المنام?page=754" > a stranger </a> in her dream includes many interpretations that were in her favor or warned her against evil in some cases.  There will be many things in common between them, and therefore their lives are characterized by peace and stability, and God knows best.</p>
<p>However, if the wise female has witnessed a heated discussion between her and this stranger, then this is considered evidence of the existence of many difficulties and obstacles that prevent her from achieving her aspirations and goals that she has tried hard to achieve but did not.  He has enough luck and skills to achieve them, and this often leads to him going through a period of despair, frustration, and loss of self-confidence.</p>
<p><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
