<div>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> in a dream means spending money and other interpretations, so we will explain it for a single woman, a married woman, a pregnant woman, a divorced woman, and a man, such as a dead nightingale in a dream, or a dead sparrow in the house, or a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-أصفر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=51" > yellow bird </a> dead, or the death of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عصفور-أزرق-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > blue sparrow </a> at the hands of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> , and more:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > a dead bird </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing <strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > a dead bird </a> in a dream</strong>, this vision shows you the bad news that will come to you, and whoever sees the dead bird, this is a sign that money has gone out of your hands and that a lot of money is spent in the wrong place or on trivial matters.<br/>And seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> getting up and flying again means that you will go to another country, and this means that you will get rid of your enemies.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> in a dream means that people want to prevent some of the things you want, and sometimes this vision shows impending sadness and fears, but if you see a dead bird flying, it shows the new beginnings that you will find in your life.<br/>And seeing a large number of <strong>dead birds in a dream</strong> shows the strength you will gain and an increase in your livelihood, but after a long period of work.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
