</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>A dream of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> is a symbol of resentment, sadness, failure, and despair. The end of the bird's life may indicate the end of some important birds. In addition, the death of the bird means changes and transformations.</p>
<p>Beautiful birds bring us hope and joy, and they fly around singing and whistling, so of course their death means the end of all that joy, and it can indicate the death of hope and joy, and it can also indicate the arrival of boring and sad times in the future.</p>
<p>One can say that birds are a symbol of love, faith, and loyalty, and their death can symbolize betrayal, distrust, and lack of trust in your loved ones.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
