</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In addition, the death of a bird can be a symbol of the evildoers in your environment, and if you see birds dying around you, it may mean that the place is not suitable for you to live.</p>
<p>Seeing a bird with a bad reputation, such as a crow or an owl, dead in a dream means that the owner will reach the status he wants after a short period, and it also indicates that the source of income of the owner of this vision will increase.</p>
<p>And anyone who sees a dead bird falling from the sky in a dream can experience such a dream to draw your attention to things that are more important in your life, and the dead bird in this dream represents something big in your life that you can't notice now, and this dream tells you that there is something in your life that you need to pay attention to and give it time and attention.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
