</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If you see a bird dying in your dream, this dream is a sign that you need to hurry to get things done, and this dream indicates that time is running out to fix something and you need to act quickly if you want to avoid any harm.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of dead birds in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الطيور-في-المنام?page=3948" > Seeing birds </a> dead in a dream is a negative vision, and anyone who sees dead birds can bring you bad luck, as well as this dream may be a warning of impending disaster.</p>
<p>Similarly, the dead bird in your dream can be a symbol of resurrection, renewal, changing situations, changing people or places, etc.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
