</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>And the death of a bird in a dream can be a sign of old habits, attitudes, or bad habits that you have left behind to become a better person, and seeing a dead bird is a sign of bad luck and despair in your future.</p>
<p>In addition, dead birds in a dream can be considered a positive symbol, because death is a fact of life, and when one life ends, another begins, so it is possible that a dream of a dead bird indicates the end of something and you may lose someone, but you will meet another person, and you may lose a job, but you will find a new one.</p>
<p>In addition, the dead bird can be considered a sign of difficult times to come, and as a sign that you should prepare well and pay attention to what awaits us in the future.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
