</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > a dead bird </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Scholars and interpreters said that seeing the death of a sparrow or <strong>a dead sparrow in a dream</strong> indicates a lack of conscience, hatred, and resentment, and seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> in a dream symbolizes a person with a hard heart and a dead conscience.<br/>Seeing the death of a bird in a dream shows the bad morals of a person and elements of selfishness and doing everything to get what he wants.<br/>Among the meanings of seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طائر-ميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=36" > dead bird </a> in a dream is not performing worship and not perfecting work.<br/>Also, <strong>the death of a bird in the dream of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-امراة-حامل?page=1441" > pregnant woman </a></strong> indicates the death of the child and miscarriage.</p>
<p>Since sparrows are a symbol of productivity, despite their small size, these birds work hard and are very energetic and always rely on themselves and their loved ones. In this sense, the death of a sparrow can be a symbol of loss of efficiency and productivity.</p>
<p>In addition, these birds represent a symbol of teamwork and cooperation, so their death can also indicate that you are not an active member of the community.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
